BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:uqTZ8NiHrcBxqfx-xVBK1
SUMMARY:You've Had It In You All Along
DTSTAMP:20260413T005345Z
DTSTART:20260417T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Artists: Barbara Earl Thomas | Tariqa Waters | Cristina Martine
	z | Robert Wade | Maikoiyo Alley-Barnes | Nahom Ghirmay “\n\nYou’ve Had It
	 In You All Along” is an affirmation of our capability to weather any stor
	m. It serves as a vital reminder that the tools required to reach your des
	tination are already etched within your spirit. We already carry the brill
	iance and the beauty of what it takes—the confidence\, the strength\, the 
	security\, the poise\, and the knowledge to achieve our goals. The grit\, 
	the rigor\, the radical ideas\, and the voice required to transcend the wo
	rld around us are not external gifts to be acquired\; they are inherent po
	wers waiting for the moment of their activation. \n\nIn the process of ove
	rcoming—when the pathway forward is unclear and the effort feels endless—i
	t is easy to lose sight of our own internal compass. When we stand face-to
	-face with rejection\, heartbreak\, or the heavy weight of difficult seaso
	ns\, this exhibition serves as a sanctuary to remind us that we have alway
	s been more than enough\, exactly as we are. Breakthroughs happen in the s
	pace where we are gentle with ourselves\, allowing for the activation of a
	n inner wisdom and intuition that has been present since our first breath.
	\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/you-ve-had-it-in-you-all
	-along/18494682/2026-04-17T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Arts & Culture
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/you-ve-had-it-in-you-all-
	along/18494682/2026-04-17T00
LOCATION:Avery Barnes Gallery\, 120 First Ave. S.\, Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-arts
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Arts & Culture
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT7H
END:VEVENT
