SUMMARY:Cynthia Brothers and Shannon Koyano Present: The Vanishing Seattle 
	Variety Show
DTSTAMP:20260413T005346Z
DTSTART:20260520T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:WEDS May 20thDOORS 7:30pm / 8pm SHOW21+$15 ADV/$18 DOSIts anoth
	er edition of the Vanishing Seattle Variety Show! With fabulous guests: dr
	ag legend and former Miss Gay Seattle Cookie Couture\\\, and writers/music
	 journalists Martin Douglas s Cobain 50 podcast! Plus comedy from Shannon 
	Koyano\\\, Vanishing Seattle trivia\\\, and special prizes and Seattle-the
	med drinks created by the citys best bartender\\\, Ramona! The VSVS is a o
	ne-of-a-kind event featuring all-local talent and blending stand-up comedy
	\\\, storytelling\\\, dazzling drag\\\, and more – in tribute to the wild 
	and weird Seattle you once knew (or still do)!**Get your tix early for thi
	s sell-out show**Co-hosted by Vanishing Seattle founder Cynthia Brothers a
